com.github.moribund.net.packets

Interface IncomingPacket

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CreateNewPlayerRequestPacket, DropItemPacket, EquipItemPacket, ExitGamePacket, ItemOnItemPacket, KeyPressedPacket, KeyUnpressedPacket, LocationPacket, LoginPacket, MouseClickedPacket, PickupItemPacket, ProjectileCollisionPacket, RotationPacket, UnequipItemPacket

    public interface IncomingPacket
    An IncomingPacket is a packet that is received by the server. This allows the client to follow the Single-Responsibility Principle as now each packet is responsible for handling itself rather than a Listener being omnipotent and handling everything.
